Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.57,ZWBT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(830,0)\pos(618,700)}我不可能和學妹成為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:57.12,ZWZJ1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,278)}和學長約會
